# Summary and Keywords

The Kochava integration with Amplitude enables bidirectional data flow, allowing marketers to share user data in real-time between platforms for attribution tracking and audience targeting, with implementation requiring the creation of a Kochava-Certified Postback that connects to Amplitude's Attribution API.

